          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Joint United Nations Programme</ENAMEX> on <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">HIV</ENAMEX>/<ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">AIDS</ENAMEX> and the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">World Health Organization</ENAMEX> based on the
