          The regional <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">models</ENAMEX> were calibrated as follows: <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</NUMEX>, plausible ranges were specified
          for <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">model</ENAMEX> parameters governing sexual behavior and biological factors (e.g., transmission
